                               ==========
                               asciifield
                               ==========


asciifield renders a starfield in your terminal, much like the good old
screensaver.


Installation
------------

There are no dependencies except for a POSIX-ish operating system. To
build the program and install it to /usr/local:

    $ make
    # make install


Running
-------

You run the program on a VT220-ish text terminal:

    $ asciifield

Refer to the manpage for all options.
